```
- Thêm message types:
```typescript
export type ExtensionMessage = ... | 
  | { type: 'GET_NOTEBOOK_ENTRIES'; payload: { topicUrl?, category?, tag?, search?, orphanOnly? } }
  | { type: 'GET_NOTEBOOK_STATS' }
  | { type: 'UPSERT_NOTEBOOK_ENTRY'; payload: NotebookEntry }
  | { type: 'DELETE_NOTEBOOK_ENTRY'; payload: { id } }
  | { type: 'ORPHAN_NOTEBOOK_BY_TOPIC'; payload: { topicUrl } }
  | { type: 'DELETE_NOTEBOOK_BY_TOPIC'; payload: { topicUrl } }
```

Sửa `entrypoints/sidepanel/views/KnowledgeView.vue`:
- Thêm import sendMessageQuiet từ lib/messaging.
- Trong `toggleSave(entry)`: 
  - Update local entries.
  - Optimistic update topic cache (chỉ saved entries).
  - Nếu next = true: tạo NotebookEntry từ entry + sourceTopicUrl, sourceTopicTitle, savedAt, gọi `sendMessageQuiet('UPSERT_NOTEBOOK_ENTRY', notebookEntry)`.
  - Nếu next = false: gọi `sendMessageQuiet('DELETE_NOTEBOOK_ENTRY', { id: entry.id })`.

Thêm `sendMessageQuiet` trong `lib/messaging.ts`:
```typescript
export function sendMessageQuiet(type: string, payload?: unknown): void {
  try {
    const p = browser.runtime.sendMessage({ type, payload });
    if (p && typeof p.catch === 'function') p.catch(() => {});
  } catch {}
}
```

